{"type": "article", "id": 17592, "title": "crescent 家具组", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-16T07:10:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110612xhciVnH2Q6bt43Br.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是澳大利亚的设计工作室 Derlot Editions 带来的系列家具，包括沙发，桌子和带衣帽架的椅子。所有的框架都是电镀不锈钢制作的，搭配蓝色或棕色的布面材料，从材料和体型上都有强烈的对比，让这组家具显得优雅，适合家庭或者商业办公环境。其中，带衣帽架的座椅上有圆形的挂钩，小巧而精致，配合座椅旁边一个圆形的不锈钢边桌，放在进门处非常实用。<a href=\"http://www.derloteditions.com/products/crescent\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261446405y6xMHTnugdlawFQ.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"735\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.89853301\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144640e6LKwmRBQWfzDpbx.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"835\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0207824\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261446418LQWxteZTigIjw2R.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"917\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.12102689\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144642aX9sEkApmH5tV7MU.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"469\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.57334963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144642DZp4zXsHmalVqbLE.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.14425428\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}